# Face Emotion Recognition

## Overview
This project focuses on building machine learning and deep learning models to recognize human facial emotions from images using both supervised and unsupervised approaches.

## Objective
To classify facial expressions such as happy, sad, angry, surprised, neutral, etc.

## Dataset
FER-2013 / facial emotion dataset.

## Methods
CNN (supervised learning), clustering and feature analysis (unsupervised learning), image preprocessing, data augmentation, model training and evaluation.

## Tools
Python, TensorFlow/Keras, OpenCV, NumPy, Matplotlib.

## Author
Reyad Taha
